txt.en: Defeat many goblins in the Vales of Anduin.
Many more goblins have been defeated. The Wilderfolk of the Vales of Anduin are grateful for your aid.

'They called it Orchost, but it is better known by another name: Goblin-town. Indeed, once it was a dwarf-delving, the High Hold of Zudr√¢ligal. But the dwarves were driven out and the goblins made it their own. They stripped out most remnants of the dwarves, leaving only the barest traces of its former ancestry.' - Gandalf the Wizard
